comments: Carter Jr. (CHI) makes contact to Anthony's (POR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Whiteside (POR) makes incidental contact with Markkanen (CHI) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Whiteside (POR) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact to Markkanen's (CHI) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Satoransky (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position on Anthony (POR) during his post move and shot attempt.
Markkanen (CHI) makes contact to Anthony's (POR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hood (POR) makes marginal contact with LaVine (CHI) that does not affect his SQBR and jump shot attempt.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact with Lillard's (POR) front that does not affect his SQBR.
Dunn (CHI) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hood (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Dunn's (CHI) drive to the basket.

Replay review of the foul called on McCollum (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  McCollum makes contact with the ball, but also to Markkanen's (CHI) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Dunn (CHI) and Lillard (POR) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Markkanen (CHI) briefly grasps Anthony's (POR) jersey during the screen but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) front during his drive to the basket.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) arm as he gathers the ball.
Hood (POR) briefly grasps LaVine (CHI) during the inbound but the contact does not affect his FOM.
LaVine (CHI) moves into McCollum (POR) and creates the marginal contact during his driving shot attempt.
Anthony (POR) briefly places a hand on Markkanen (CHI) during the inbound before immediately sliding it off.
Whiteside (POR) places a forearm against Carter Jr.'s (CHI) back, but does not extend it and dislodge him from his rebounding position during the long rebound.
Whiteside (POR) makes marginal contact with Markkanen (CHI) that does not affect his shot attempt near the rim.
Whiteside (POR) makes hand on ball contact as Markkanen (CHI) gathers the loose ball and a held ball is whistled.
